---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`Education | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="My educational background" />
		<style>
			main {
				max-width: 1200px;
			}
			
			.page-header {
				padding: 4rem 0 3rem 0;
			}
			
			.page-title {
				font-size: 3.5rem;
				font-weight: 800;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				color: var(--text-primary);
			}
			
			.page-subtitle {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				color: var(--text-tertiary);
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}
			
			.intro-text {
				font-size: 1.125rem;
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				line-height: 1.8;
				max-width: 900px;
				margin-bottom: 4rem;
			}
			
			.education-list {
				margin-bottom: 4rem;
			}
			
			.education-item {
				padding: 2rem;
				background: var(--bg-secondary);
				border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
				border-radius: 16px;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}
			
			.education-header {
				display: flex;
				align-items: flex-start;
				gap: 1rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}
			
			.education-icon {
				width: 3rem;
				height: 3rem;
				background: var(--accent);
				border-radius: 8px;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				color: white;
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}
			
			.education-content {
				flex: 1;
			}
			
			.education-degree {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				color: var(--text-primary);
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				font-weight: 700;
			}
			
			.education-school {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				font-size: 1.125rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}
			
			.education-date {
				color: var(--text-tertiary);
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}
			
			.education-description {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				line-height: 1.7;
			}
			
			.nav-links {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				padding: 2rem 0;
				border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
			}
			
			.nav-link {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				text-decoration: none;
				transition: color 0.2s ease;
			}
			
			.nav-link:hover {
				color: var(--accent);
			}
			
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.page-title {
					font-size: 2.5rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="page-header">
				<h1 class="page-title">Education</h1>
				<p class="page-subtitle">I learned a lot, but the real learning happens in the code editor!</p>
			</section>

			<p class="intro-text">
				Education has always been the cornerstone of my journey into the tech world. My academic path 
				in Computer Applications provided me with a strong foundation in computer science and software 
				development. The journey has been complemented by hands-on projects, continuous learning, and 
				professional certifications, enabling me to build practical skills and a deep understanding of 
				modern technological solutions.
			</p>

			<div class="education-list">
				<div class="education-item">
					<div class="education-header">
						<div class="education-icon">üéì</div>
						<div class="education-content">
							<h3 class="education-degree">Master of Computer Applications (MCA)</h3>
							<p class="education-school">Jawaharlal College of Engineering (JCE)</p>
							<p class="education-date">2013 - 2016</p>
							<p class="education-description">
								GPA: 8.23/10 ‚Ä¢ Focused on advanced programming, software engineering, and system design. 
								Built strong foundations in data structures, algorithms, and enterprise application development.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="education-item">
					<div class="education-header">
						<div class="education-icon">üéì</div>
						<div class="education-content">
							<h3 class="education-degree">Bachelor of Computer Applications (BCA)</h3>
							<p class="education-school">SBRR Mahajana First Grade College</p>
							<p class="education-date">2010 - 2013</p>
							<p class="education-description">
								Comprehensive undergraduate program covering programming fundamentals, database systems, 
								web technologies, and software development methodologies.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="education-item">
					<div class="education-header">
						<div class="education-icon">üìú</div>
						<div class="education-content">
							<h3 class="education-degree">Professional Certifications</h3>
							<p class="education-school">Continuous Learning</p>
							<p class="education-date">2016 - Present</p>
							<p class="education-description">
								<strong>Java & Testing</strong> - Abcforjava<br>
								<strong>ASP.NET & C#</strong> - United Latino Students Association<br>
								Committed to continuous learning through industry certifications and professional development programs.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="nav-links">
				<a href="/experience" class="nav-link">
					<span>‚Üê</span>
					<span>Experience</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/contact" class="nav-link">
					<span>Contact</span>
					<span>‚Üí</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
